Death Becomes Her;;61;;54;;PG-13;;When a novelist loses her man to a movie star and former friend, she winds up in a psychiatric hospital. Years later, she returns home to confront the now-married couple, looking radiant. Her ex-husband's new wife wants to know her secret, and discovers that she has been taking a mysterious drug which grants eternal life to the person who drinks it. The actress follows suit, but discovers that immortality has a price.;;Fantasy,Comedy;;Robert Zemeckis;;1992;;Meryl Streep,Bruce Willis,Goldie Hawn,Isabella Rossellini,Ian Ogilvy,Adam Storke,Nancy Fish,Michelle Johnson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_becomes_her